data.title: The Faculty of Business and Finance (FBF) of Kampar Campus celebrated the joyful spirit of Raya with an Eid-al-Fitri Luncheon 2024,...
data.meta_description:
16 likes, 0 comments - utarnet1 on May 6, 2024: "The Faculty of Business and Finance (FBF) of Kampar Campus celebrated the joyful spirit of Raya with an Eid-al-Fitri Luncheon 2024, organised on 25 April 2024 at Block H, UTAR Kampar Campus.

By creating a unique multicultural environment, the Raya luncheon encircled the FBF academics and staff in a harmonious atmosphere and bolstered their bonds and friendships. Besides, the luncheon was also filled with fun mini games and activities such as Malaysian traditional games Batu Seremban and Congkak, Guess the Raya Food and lucky draw sessions. 

Also present at the Raya luncheon were UTAR Vice President for Student Development and Alumni Relations Prof Dr Choong Chee Keong, FBF Dean Assoc Prof Dr Au Yong Hui Nee, FBF Department of Commerce and Accountancy Head Sonia Johanthan, the project leader Che Siti Lazrina Md Lazim, FBF academic and staff.".
